What you need to know:

Forward Brian Marita netted in the 55th minute to put the mailmen ahead following a swift counter attack which started in Posta Rangers' halfSecond half substitute Oscar Wamalwa then scored in the 94th minute to draw his side level and secure a point for the visitorsAfter the chaotic scenes, Ouma's penalty came off the post to the disappointment of Ulinzi fans and the technical bench